        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" , "Rationale: LRFN5 was enriched in postsynaptic density fractions.\n\n15/01/2018 Pim\n- LRFN5 displays a (low affinity) interaction with the PSD-95 protein (Fig.4H)\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Figure legend\nfig 4D. Enrichment of SALM3 and SALM5 proteins in postsynaptic (PSD) fractions of adult rat brain (6 weeks)." ;
